data.description: Inside this beautiful 3 bedroom, 3 bathroom home you'll find fresh paint, new floors, and vaulted ceilings bolstered by natural light through east and south facing windows. Outside, enjoy a designated garden area on just shy of a quarter acre corner lot which backs up to natural green space. With just a few exterior updates this home with be the perfect equity builder for first time home buyers. New roof and siding? Seller will replace roof and siding for a full price offer.
